reviewText:
As a fan of the Titanic and since I wanted to play a hidden object game, I thought: Why not.

Here's why not:

- Only Windowed mode looks bearable
- Hidden Objexts are often rendered so badly, you spot them directly
- A horribly, unlikable main character
- poor music choice

Also its definitly too expensive for the little it offers.

reviewText: I enjoyed Titanic. It was interesting, but simple. If you're in the mood for something that is not overly taxing to brain (after work relaxing entertainment), this would be it.
